ic composition of the Trucial Coast in 1901; the camel convoy\u2019s route from Abu Dhabi to the Qatar Peninsula; life of Coastal citizens in India and their relationship with other communities there and resulting mutual influence. The book also focuses on the Trucial Oman Levies; Zanzibar and its trade relations with the people of the Coast; locust control operations and the beginning of radio transmission in the region &#8212; Sawt (Voice) Al-Sahel; and on international broadcasts targeting the region with the intention of effecting political, social and cultural changes at that time.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3965,"template":"","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false},"product_cat":[15],"product_tag":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3964"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3965"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3964"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=3964"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=3964"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}